column15: All Season Luxury White Duck Down Duvet Comforter Insert BOKSER HOME  Made of 700-fill power premium white duck down100% cotton sateen shellCorner loops hold a duvet cover securely in placeBaffle box construction keeps the fill evenly distributedGenerously sized to ensure you won't have empty corners in your duvet coverskuId: 200221347The BOKSER HOME All Season Down Duvet Insert is made with premium ultra lofty 700 fill power white duck down. Encompassed in a soft 100% cotton sateen shell, the baffle box construction keeps the fill evenly distributed throughout the entire duvet. The BOKSER HOME down duvet insert stays fluffy over time and is slightly oversized so that your bed always looks and feels extra lofty and comfy. With a mid-weight fill, the all season down comforter offers year-round cozy comfort. Our Down Duvet inserts are 90% premium white duck down and 10% feather. Machine washable and dryable, the BOKSER HOME All Season Duck Down Duvet Comforter Insert has corner loops to hold your duvet cover in place. The BOKSER down duvet insert is an easy, cozy, and beautiful way to add warmth and sophistication to your bedroom.  Twin Fill Weight 27 oz  Full/Queen Fill Weight 35 oz  King/Cal King Fill Weight 42 ozWe use premium white duck down and feathers in all BOKSER HOME products due to the extraordinary warmth-to-weight ratio. Our down and feather manufacturing process includes multiple wash cycles to remove any impurities and ensure cleanliness. All BOKSER down products are independently tested and proudly certified by the Responsible Down Standard. The RDS guarantees the ethical sourcing of our products by respecting the animal-welfare practices in down and feather production, from the farm to the final product. We started BOKSER HOME to help more people love their bedding. We create home décor that is beautiful, responsibly sourced, and affordable. Our goal is to make the highest quality bedding at the lowest possible price.   read more

column15: DB Chez Vous - Microgel Synthetic Down Duvet, Hypoallergenic, Queen Size, White  Microgel duvets are perfect alternatives to down this synthetic fiber comes from a new spinning technology, i.e. a microgel fiber is very fine, 100x finer than a human hair , which gives it a very soft and silky touch. The microgel duvet is comparable to down for its fluffiness and softness. Very fluffy, the latter is also easy to maintain because it washes and dries easily without the risk of creating agglomerates. Due to its finesse, it is also an excellent product for people looking for a duvet that eliminates as much moisture as possible during the night. column15: DB Chez Vous - Microgel Synthetic Down Duvet, Hypoallergenic, Double Size, White  Microgel duvets are perfect alternatives to down this synthetic fiber comes from a new spinning technology, i.e. a microgel fiber is very fine, 100x finer than a human hair , which gives it a very soft and silky touch. The microgel duvet is comparable to down for its fluffiness and softness. Very fluffy, the latter is also easy to maintain because it washes and dries easily without the risk of creating agglomerates. Due to its finesse, it is also an excellent product for people looking for a duvet that eliminates as much moisture as possible during the night. Ideal for those   Who want the feeling of silky down Who prefer washable down Who are envious of a superb duvet but with a small budget  Specifications   Microgel fiber Hypoallergenic 100% Cotton 233 Threads Shell Hermetic Tiles 300 g/m2 Thickness 2.5''  Certificates   Oeko-Tex Hypoallergenic, laboratory tested, absence of toxic substances and without risk to consumer health  Washing and care instructions  Machine wash at 30 degrees, tumble dry low or no heat, do not iron, do not bleach, can also be dry cleaned.skuId: 200743663    read more

column15: It's like a pillowcase to protect your duvet or comforter, and an affordable way to freshen up the look of your bedding. A simple zipper closure makes it easy to slip your duvet in and out, and corner ties prevent your insert from bunching up while you sleep. Duvet insert / comforter sold separately. Designed to perform flawlessly in the bedroom, dorm room, children's room, RV, cabin and vacation homes.  WHAT IS IT? It's like a pillowcase to protect your duvet insert or duvet filler. Our super soft duvet covers and duvet sets are an affordable competitor to any linen duvet cover. A simple zipper closure makes it easy to slip your duvet in and out, and corner ties keep your insert in place while you sleep. Down alternative duvet insert sold separately. SANDWASHED FOR SOFTNESS  Our popular, cooling duvet cover is now available sandwashed for a lived-in feel right out of the packaging. Using our unique sandwashing process, this duvet cover can compare to any hotel duvet cover. WHY CHOOSE BARE? Because our chic farmhouse duvet cover will give you satin duvet cover comfort at a "Wow!" worthy price. EASY CARE  Simply toss your duvet set cover in the washing machine. Wash it in cold water with similar colors and tumble dry on low.   Dimensions  Twin/Twin XL  1 Duvet Cover 66" x 92", 1 Standard Sham 26" x 20" Full  1 Duvet Cover 82" x 86", 2 Standard Shams 26" x 20" Queen  1 Duvet Cover 90" x 92", 2 Standard Shams 26" x 20" Oversized Queen  1 Duvet Cover 98" x 98", 2 Standard Shams 26" x 20" King/California King  1 Duvet Cover 90" x 104", 2 King Shams 36" x 20" Oversized King  1 Duvet Cover 98" x 116", 2 King Shams 36" x 20"   skuId: 200068025   read more

Treat yourself to luxury bedding. Be warned, though You may never be an early bird again! KING SIZE DUVET SET MEASUREMENTS 1 DUVET (104"x90") and 2 Pillow Sham (21"x36"). column15: It's like a pillowcase to protect your duvet or comforter, and an affordable way to freshen the look of your bedding. Add a touch of glamor and style to your sleeping space with our sumptuous Shaggy Duvet Cover. Duvet insert/comforter sold separately.  FEATURES    A luxurious 45mm plush front, crystal velvet back, and is soft and durable. Contains a hidden zipper closure on the back side with corner ties to prevent your duvet from bunching up while you sleep. Breathable for year-round comfort and can be used without an insert in warmer weather. Consists of long lasting quality with supreme softness to give you the coziest duvet cover you will ever own.  Easy Care   Turn your shaggy duvet cover inside-out and machine wash cold on a gentle cycle. Non-chlorine bleach only as needed. Tumble dry low. Do not dry or iron.  Specifications   Comes with one shaggy duvet cover.
